      ],
      "motivation": "Eliminate `ttg.convert_layout` operations that survived RemoveLayoutConversions (ch.13) by **rematerializing** the convert's source backward slice in the target encoding, or by **hoisting** the convert above type-widening ops.",
      "reference_chapter": "ch.14.LayoutRematerialization",
